1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,900
=Episode 21=

23
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,279
Look at Zhou Zeyang's loser state today.

24
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:51,199
How did we fall for him back then?

25
00:01:51,260 --> 00:01:53,759
I didn't expect beating up a scumbag
could feel so satisfying.

26
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:56,319
So love yourself first.

27
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,720
We don't need to please anyone.

28
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,119
Say no to female rivalry.

29
00:01:59,275 --> 00:02:00,355
Start with us.

30
00:02:00,425 --> 00:02:00,985
Mm.

31
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,320
Shanshan, hand me the knife.

32
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,279
Shanshan?

33
00:02:17,559 --> 00:02:18,520
Why are you here?

34
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:21,240
What do you want to cut? I'll do it.

35
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:34,800
It's alright that a youthful and beautiful
college student like me can't cook.

36
00:02:35,119 --> 00:02:37,360
But is that how someone your age cut?

37
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,119
What do you mean "my age"?

38
00:02:39,119 --> 00:02:40,159
I'm not even 30.

39
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,725
Sorry, old chap.

40
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,240
I forgot you're the younger version now.

41
00:02:44,712 --> 00:02:45,520
Old chap?

42
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,559
Old chap means...

43
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,679
Boss.

44
00:02:54,999 --> 00:02:56,119
Aren't you Mr. Qin?

45
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,080
I can also call you Old Chap Qin.

46
00:02:59,150 --> 00:02:59,949
Oh.

47
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,910
I haven't even properly thanked you

48
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,760
about the raw material incident.

49
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,399
Zhuang Yan, thank you.

50
00:03:09,225 --> 00:03:10,184
How rare.

51
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:14,920
The future you always looks at me
with a frustrated expression.

52
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,960
It's like you want to pack me up

53
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,760
and throw this shameful niece

54
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,279
off the earth.

55
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,399
I didn't expect the younger you

56
00:03:22,399 --> 00:03:24,240
to say such sensible things.

57
00:03:27,119 --> 00:03:28,800
No need to apologize so much.

58
00:03:29,159 --> 00:03:31,999
You may not be a likable uncle,

59
00:03:32,399 --> 00:03:34,320
but at least you're a competent one.

60
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,599
All these years,
you couldn't give emotional support,

61
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,159
but your financial support was on point.

62
00:03:38,999 --> 00:03:41,159
So I'm not completely useless.

63
00:03:41,999 --> 00:03:43,760
Then why won't you like me?

64
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:47,800
Because I gaslighted myself

65
00:03:48,119 --> 00:03:49,350
to only like your money,

66
00:03:49,350 --> 00:03:50,559
not you.

67
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,719
What's "gaslight"?

68
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,950
Talking to someone socially clueless
like you is exhausting.

69
00:03:57,439 --> 00:04:00,320
"Gaslight" means
doing mental conditioning for yourself.

70
00:04:02,839 --> 00:04:05,200
Doing mental conditioning for yourself

71
00:04:05,279 --> 00:04:07,240
shows that I caused you great trouble,

72
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,320
so you have to
control yourself from liking me.

73
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,679
Doesn't that also mean

74
00:04:11,679 --> 00:04:13,480
you have some feelings for me?

75
00:04:14,412 --> 00:04:16,413
(You even learned reverse reasoning.)

76
00:04:16,862 --> 00:04:18,359
(Cunning romantic.)

77
00:04:18,359 --> 00:04:19,320
So

78
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,919
do you like me?

79
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:21,919
You...

80
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:23,312
Put the knife down first.

81
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,200
I don't hate you.

82
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:30,520
No.

83
00:04:30,799 --> 00:04:33,120
Is it so hard to just say you like me?

84
00:04:37,162 --> 00:04:38,443
I'll only ask once.

85
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:40,599
I want to hear the truth.

86
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,479
Fine, I admit I...

87
00:04:45,359 --> 00:04:46,839
I like you a little bit,

88
00:04:47,712 --> 00:04:49,279
but I can't ruin my reputation.

89
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:51,100
So there's still no chance between us.

90
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:52,919
Give up, Boss.

91
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,239
Hey.

92
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,080
I refuse to be just your boss.

93
00:05:04,087 --> 00:05:08,062
♪Watching movies, sharing popcorn,
and having fun together♪

94
00:05:08,150 --> 00:05:11,212
♪The warmth under the umbrella
while walking in the rain♪

95
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:15,600
♪Those scenes
replay in my mind like a film♪

96
00:05:15,712 --> 00:05:19,775
♪All unique marks of love♪

97
00:05:20,287 --> 00:05:24,250
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

98
00:05:24,250 --> 00:05:27,850
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

99
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:31,637
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

100
00:05:31,712 --> 00:05:35,487
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

101
00:05:37,125 --> 00:05:38,420
What's your purpose in seeing me?

102
00:05:39,987 --> 00:05:41,227
I'll give you three minutes.

103
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:45,919
Qin Mo.

104
00:05:47,479 --> 00:05:48,719
I...

105
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:51,399
I've been competing with you
for so long.

106
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,479
I...

107
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,279
I admit.

108
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:57,320
I admit.

109
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:57,799
Two minutes.

110
00:05:57,799 --> 00:05:59,239
I lost.

111
00:06:01,599 --> 00:06:04,560
I've accumulated
a lot of connections in Haicheng.

112
00:06:05,174 --> 00:06:08,294
And all the equipment I bought
for the food factory are state-of-the-art.

113
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,320
I'll give them all to you.

114
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,359
One minute.

115
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:13,711
No, Qin Mo.

116
00:06:14,875 --> 00:06:16,875
The idea to intercept your palm oil deal

117
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,737
was Zhou Zeyang's.

118
00:06:19,387 --> 00:06:21,387
He tricked my money to use against you.

119
00:06:21,479 --> 00:06:24,200
The money you paid for the palm oil
went straight into his account.

120
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,399
We were all victims.

121
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,799
He's the real conman.

122
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,000
Get me out of here.

123
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,279
I'll help you take him down.

124
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,400
I'm begging you.

125
00:06:35,762 --> 00:06:38,281
Do you really think
Zhou Zeyang can take that money?

126
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,080
Qin Mo.

127
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,120
Time's up.

128
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,919
Qin Mo, please give me a way out.

129
00:06:43,919 --> 00:06:45,120
I'm begging you.

130
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:48,000
I'll give you the money
I kept in overseas and Swiss banks.

131
00:06:48,039 --> 00:06:49,399
Please let me out.

132
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,200
I'm begging you.

133
00:06:51,039 --> 00:06:51,799
Zhang Guolong.

134
00:06:52,479 --> 00:06:53,680
Truth hurts.

135
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:55,880
You're really not fit for business.

136
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,320
You're only fit for prison.

137
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,479
Qin Mo.

138
00:06:58,599 --> 00:06:59,399
Qin Mo!

139
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:01,900
Let me out!

140
00:07:02,162 --> 00:07:03,350
Ah!

141
00:07:10,937 --> 00:07:11,297
Get in.

142
00:07:11,362 --> 00:07:12,083
Okay.

143
00:07:14,425 --> 00:07:15,105
Sir.

144
00:07:15,479 --> 00:07:17,350
No. 43, Zhongke Road, Hailian District.

145
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,760
Shanshan.

146
00:07:58,700 --> 00:07:59,460
Shanshan.

147
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,080
Mom?

148
00:08:03,562 --> 00:08:04,523
Qin Jiamin.

149
00:08:15,799 --> 00:08:17,159
Zhou Zeyang.

150
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,080
Is it strange?

151
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,200
Zhuang Yan.

152
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,799
What do you want?

153
00:08:25,039 --> 00:08:27,239
My plan was perfect.

154
00:08:27,239 --> 00:08:29,399
I worked hard to manage everything.

155
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:30,479
Zhuang Yan.

156
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:34,619
You jumped in and ruined everything,
do you know that?

157
00:08:35,125 --> 00:08:36,564
I'm confused.

158
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,359
Qin Mo protects you.

159
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:41,320
You also won
Shanshan and Qin Jiamin's hearts.

160
00:08:41,479 --> 00:08:42,519
And me?

161
00:08:43,237 --> 00:08:44,404
I gave my all.

162
00:08:44,450 --> 00:08:46,011
Who cared about me?

163
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:49,719
You're corrupt,

164
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:52,239
trying to rise using women.

165
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:54,400
You accuse me of rising with women.

166
00:08:55,125 --> 00:08:55,924
And?

167
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,680
What about you?

168
00:09:00,359 --> 00:09:02,239
How innocent are you?

169
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,662
You also used your relations

170
00:09:04,662 --> 00:09:06,400
with Qin Mo and Shanshan

171
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,999
to get this far, didn't you?

172
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:10,587
People born with a silver spoon like you

173
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:13,350
act all high and mighty every day.

174
00:09:14,119 --> 00:09:16,200
What right do you have to criticize me?

175
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:17,719
Why?

176
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,800
You wouldn't let me rise,

177
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,962
so I'll pull you all down.

178
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,759
Don't worry.

179
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,600
Qin Mo is next.

180
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,599
Hello?

181
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,519
Qin Mo, it's me.

182
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,479
Zhou Zeyang?

183
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,280
Zhuang Yan is with me.

184
00:10:37,479 --> 00:10:38,280
Manying.

185
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,759
Manying.

186
00:10:41,479 --> 00:10:42,320
Manying.

187
00:10:52,359 --> 00:10:52,800
Manying.

188
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,440
Manying.

189
00:11:27,725 --> 00:11:28,599
No.

190
00:12:08,999 --> 00:12:09,839
Manying.

191
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,639
Are you okay?

192
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:12,479
I'm fine.

193
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:15,625
Don't be afraid.

194
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,999
I'm here.

195
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:38,588
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

196
00:12:38,713 --> 00:12:42,025
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

197
00:12:42,188 --> 00:12:45,775
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

198
00:12:46,075 --> 00:12:49,363
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

199
00:12:49,588 --> 00:12:53,213
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

200
00:12:53,375 --> 00:12:56,713
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

201
00:12:56,788 --> 00:13:00,500
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

202
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:04,413
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

203
00:13:04,475 --> 00:13:10,525
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

204
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:18,438
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

205
00:13:18,725 --> 00:13:23,000
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

206
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:26,300
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

207
00:13:26,375 --> 00:13:30,675
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

208
00:13:30,738 --> 00:13:34,388
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

209
00:13:34,388 --> 00:13:37,950
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

210
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:41,263
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

211
00:13:41,263 --> 00:13:45,013
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

212
00:13:45,013 --> 00:13:51,725
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
